<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1"?>
<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Virtual
File System</application></title>

<para>Installez <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Virtual File System</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix ORBit-2.0` \
    --libexecdir=`pkg-config --variable=prefix ORBit-2.0`/sbin \
    --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome --disable-gtk-doc &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>
